Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.52,0:04:22.16,Nadpis,,0,0,0,, 6\N Král pirátů
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.66,0:04:51.70,Nadpis,,0,0,0,,Taira no Kijomori\NMACUJAMA Ken'iči
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.16,0:04:48.62,Nadpis,,0,0,0,,{\fs45}český překlad     SONMI    7. 10. 2015
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:55.82,Nadpis,,0,0,0,,Minamoto no Jošimoto\NTAMAKI Hiroši
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:59.82,Nadpis,,0,0,0,,Sato Norikijo\NFUDŽIKI Naohito
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.13,0:05:07.87,Nadpis,,0,0,0,,Taira no Tadamasa\NTOJOHARA Kosuke
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.44,0:05:46.24,Nadpis,,0,0,0,,Minamoto no Joritomo/ vypravěč\NOKADA Masaki
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.60,0:06:13.07,Nadpis,,0,0,0,,Taira no Tadamori\NNAKAI Kiiči
